88
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:19,350
Kau sudah bangun?
Apa kepalamu masih sakit?

89
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,180
Kau berjaga malam
karena mengkhawatirkan itu?

90
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:27,300
