dan terkena angin.

91
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,470
Mungkin kau masuk angin.

92
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:34,950
Aku tak apa-apa.

93
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,590
Kembalilah ke kamar dan istirahat.

94
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,480
